These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-1::.
Movie-Genre: action, disaster
Transport: bus, car
1. Transport:bus is in an even position##4
2. Transport:car == Movie-Genre:disaster##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2      |
| Movie-Genre   | disaster | action |
| Transport     | car    | bus   |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-2::.
City: liverpool, colone
House: cottage, victorian
1. House:cottage is in an odd position##4
2. City:colone is on the left of City:liverpool##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |       2       |
| City   | colone | liverpool        |
| House      | cottage  | victorian |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-3::.
City: colone, boston
Sport: tennis, surfing
1. Sport:tennis is in an odd position##4
2. City:boston is on the left of City:colone##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |
| City   | boston    | colone |
| Sport   | tennis | surfing |

